data.description:
Gorgeous 1 story Next Gen home (The Home within a Home), corner lot with curb appeal. Perfect for multigenerational families, parents, college students, etc. Next Gen concept includes a private suite with a living area, bedroom, kitchenette with breakfast bar, private bath and stackable washer and dryer connection. Open-concept. Has been well maintained and features granite countertops, ceramic tile in common areas, bathrooms, entrance and laundry room, carpet in living room and bedrooms, entire home has been freshly painted. This home has 2 living areas, split bedrooms for even more privacy, high ceilings, large backyard with an extended patio, 3 car garage with epoxy flooring, 2 tankless water heaters, updated lighting, 2 new garbage disposals, new faucets, fence newly stained, new gutters, new roof and gas line hookup in the backyard. Master bathroom has separate shower and garden jetted tub.
Resort-style subdivision with jogging trails, tennis courts, community pool and more.
